{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01NDwhUPVTDgYtAtViXRafzt","type":"tool_result","content":"   175→\n   176→### F-041: Web Message Timestamp Display\n   177→- DECISION: `.message` changed from `display: block` to `display: flex; flex-direction: column` — allows timestamp span to sit at bottom with `text-align: right` without absolute positioning; `.message .body` class extracts `white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word` (was on `.message`) since flex parent doesn't need it.\n   178→- DECISION: `formatTimestamp()` uses `new Date()` at call time (moment of render) — captures accurate send time for user messages and receive time for assistant messages; called inside `createMessageElement()`.\n   179→- DECISION: `.message-timestamp` uses only CSS vars (`--muted`) — dark mode auto-switches without explicit `@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark)` override block; same pattern as `.kbd`, `.empty-state`, `.scroll-to-bottom`, `.copy-btn`."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2e2c5d48-2c5c-4924-9a4c-071d0c254490","uuid":"c84b6eac-2a76-462f-9e1e-1f568a7f7024","timestamp":"2026-03-23T10:19:52.445Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/CLAUDE.md","content":"\n### F-041: Web Message Timestamp Display\n- DECISION: `.message` changed from `display: block` to `display: flex; flex-direction: column` — allows timestamp span to sit at bottom with `text-align: right` without absolute positioning; `.message .body` class extracts `white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word` (was on `.message`) since flex parent doesn't need it.\n- DECISION: `formatTimestamp()` uses `new Date()` at call time (moment of render) — captures accurate send time for user messages and receive time for assistant messages; called inside `createMessageElement()`.\n- DECISION: `.message-timestamp` uses only CSS vars (`--muted`) — dark mode auto-switches without explicit `@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark)` override block; same pattern as `.kbd`, `.empty-state`, `.scroll-to-bottom`, `.copy-btn`.","numLines":5,"startLine":175,"totalLines":204}}}
